snippet.textDisplay: Wow I am speechless this was a total banger.  Definitely this song gonna be in my grooving while working list now..... Loved this one and the way Armaan's and TRI.BE girls voices matched was damn good. And as always Allu Arjun moves took my heart away and not mention the way both the girls and Allu Arjun synced. Specially that one move where he was making korean heart symbol and the girls where doing namaste Ioved it. And wow listening korean, Hindi, Telugu all together in one song was cherry on the top for me...... Just returned from my hectic work and listened to this and trust me when I say I was grooving along with this song...... I am loving this one.....
